Author: HansakaMadushan
Title: [BOUNTY] BITSCREENER - THE #1 CRYPTO TRACKER - [REAL PRODUCTS] [REAL ICO]
Body: BitScreener is a finance focused unified platform of cryptocurrency and stock tracker powered by blockchain. It integrates data of separated spaces of stock and cryptocurrency into a single platform, allowing traders and investors to track their investments across the domains seamlessly. At the same time, writers and researchers can contribute new content to the system for rewards. BitScreener leverages the blockchain incentivization mechanism for user engagement and content quality. The visualization tools . of the data subsystem support writers to create new content easily within the platform. Once published, the newly generated content is transparently evaluated by the community for rewards. The two subsystems data and decentralized content of the system are weaved together, making BitScreener a unique ecosystem evolving overtime.

Author: chanakaweerasingaha
Title: [BOUNTY] BITSCREENER - THE #1 CRYPTO TRACKER - [REAL PRODUCTS] [REAL ICO]
Body: BitScreener is a finance-focused unified platform of cryptocurrency and stock tracker powered by blockchain. It integrates data of separated spaces of stock and cryptocurrency into a single platform, allowing traders and investors to track their investments across the domains seamlessly. At the same time, writers and researchers can contribute new content to the system for rewards. BitScreener leverages the blockchain incentivization mechanism for user engagement and content quality. The visualization tools charts, table, news, etc of the data subsystem support writers to create new content easily within the platform. Once published, the newly generated content is transparently evaluated by the community for rewards.

Title: [BOUNTY] BITSCREENER - THE #1 CRYPTO TRACKER - [REAL PRODUCTS] [REAL ICO]
Body: BitScreener Point Once the newly created content is verified and accepted by reviewers, it is fed to our BSP unit for calculating the points which later will be converted to BITX. On the other hand, the rejected article is also awarded some points, which is less compared with the accepted article, to appreciate the effort of the writer. We also emphasize that the published content will be paid additional points based on the number of upvotes by readers over its lifetime. Our system calculates the points based on the consensus feedback of users who consume the content.

Body: BitScreener is a finance focused unified platform of cryptocurrency and stock tracker powered by blockchain. It integrates data of separated spaces of stock and cryptocurrency into a single platform, allowing traders and investors to track their investments across the domains seamlessly. At the same time, writers and researchers can contribute new content to the system for rewards. BitScreener leverages the blockchain incentivization mechanism for user engagement and content quality.

Author: Hodlillo
Title: [BOUNTY] BITSCREENER - THE #1 CRYPTO TRACKER - [REAL PRODUCTS] [REAL ICO]
Body: BitScreener $BITX  Dünyanın ilk blokzinciri tabanlı Finansal Data Ekosistemidir. Dünya genelinde 2000 den fazla coin/ico ların ve 100000+ fazla marketin kolayca takip edilebilecek bir platform oluşumudur.  Hedefleri; anlık olarak borsalarla uyumlu verileri sunabilmek, Adil olmayan ve güncelliğini kaybetmiş bilgilerin yatırımcıları yanlış yönlendirmesinin önüne geçmek, kripto paralar ile marketleri tek platform da birleştirmektir.  BitScreener ekosistemi birbirinden önemli dört teknolojinin harmanlanması ile karşımıza çıkmaktadır. Bunlar; Data toplama ve kıymetlendirme (örnek coinmarket cap verileri ) , Finansal marketlere erişim ( örnek marketwatch verileri) , Finans sistemini yorumlama ve değerlendirme (örnek Wikipedia, Stockover verileri) ve Blok zinciri tabanlı olmak. BitScreener ekosistemi yukarıdaki teknolojileri bir arada tutacak teknoloji geliştiriyor ve Doğruluk ve adalet ilkesi ile yüksek kaliteli finans bilgilerini müşterilerine sunmayı amaçlıyor.  $BITX Finansal ekosistemde yatırımcılarına yüksek karlar getirebilecek yatırımlara yönlendirmek için profesyonel araştırmacılar tarafından BitScreener platformunda sunulan bilgileri satın almaya yarayacak en ekonomik ödeme sistemidir.  $BITX Coin dağılımı titizlikle planlanmıştır. Bu planlamada özellikle yaşanabilecek pump ve dump ların önüne geçmektir. Toplamda maksimum 450.000 adet BITX oluşturulmuştur ,Dağılım: Halka Arz : % 31 oranında halka arz 5 mayıs -20 temmuz arasında satış olacaktır. (1 etherium =7154 BITX) Satış sürecinde satılamayan koinler yakılacaktır. Madencilik Payı: % 20 oranında madenciliğe ayrılmıştır. Madencilik tıpkı bitcoin teknolojisi gibi olacaktır. Madencilik süresi yaklaşık 15 yıl sürecektir. Bonus payı : % 4 oranında bonus olarak dağıtılacaktır. Gelecek Planlaması Payı: % 30 oranında ayrılmıştır. En önemlisi önümüzdeki 2 yıl boyunca cüzdanda kilit altında olacak ve piyasaya sürülmeyecektir. Takım Payı: % 15 oranında takım çalışanlarına ayrılmıştır. En önemlisi Borsaya girdikten sonra takım çalışanlarına ayrılan pay 6 ile 12 ay boyunca cüzdanda kilit altında olacak ve bu süre boyunca piyasaya sürülemeyecektir. $BITX , BitScreener Ltd şirketi tarafından Singapur’da, 2018106714 kayıt numarası ile yasal olarak yönetilmektedir. Author: ZumbiLe
Title: [BOUNTY] BITSCREENER - THE #1 CRYPTO TRACKER - [REAL PRODUCTS] [REAL ICO]
Body: Alert or notification features of any financial application play a decisive role in informing the trader on the movement of the financial instrument. Traders typically want to be the first to get updates on any events associated with their investment vehicle, so that they be prepared with their investments ahead of others. For this reason, notification is a prioritized feature on our platform. The current BitScreener App allows users to get price alerts, volume alerts, and market cap alerts, right on their mobile devices. To make this possible, the backend server with the data collector is carefully configured so that the alert can be triggered by the specified price or volume movement of cryptos directly from exchanges. For example, users can set a price alert for LTC EUR on the exchange GDAX and be confident they will be notified in real-time from the exchange. Similarly, users are also able to set a volume change alert for a coin with information from nearly 100 crypto exchanges.

Title: [BOUNTY] BITSCREENER - THE #1 CRYPTO TRACKER - [REAL PRODUCTS] [REAL ICO]
Body: https://i.imgur.com/SBXWdug.png  ANN | WEBSITE | /bitscreener_whitepaper]WHITEPAPER | Facebook | Twitter | Medium | Telegram  BITSCREENER ROCKET PROGRAM HAS ENDED  Earn token BITX through App referral, Twitter, and Facebook bounty  DESCRIPTIONS:  - BitScreener users will be rewarded with STAKES; each STAKE will be converted to token BITX (see formula below). - The program is counted as months, starting from September 01, 2018 - Total BITX allocation for each month: 8,000 BITX for Twitter and Facebook, and Edit Suggestion to the coins' profile in our website - The rule for each month, including the total BITX for each month, is subject to change and will be announced before the month starts - Your STAKEs will be summarized at: https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/13Ejixlb_G45hj3mtt57TeCFPmgNF_DNagg_v-iOIoZc/edit?usp=sharing   HOW TO CONVERT STAKES TO BITX AFTER EACH MONTH:  Your final number of BITX after each month = Total number of BITX allocated in this month * Number of STAKES you earned in this month / Total number of STAKES all participants (on all campaigns) earned in this month Note: By this formula, one STAKE can be converted to more or less than 1 BITX, depending on the number of total number of STAKES earned    Check your stakes on this SPREADSHEET    Twitter Campaign (Started on Jul 23rd) Twitter Instructions: Requirement: Your twitter account must have at least 200 real followers   How to Join: Step 1: Reply a new message on this thread with your BitcoinTalk username, profile link, Telegram ID & ETH Address to confirm your identity We will check this info manually to send Tokens to the right person later Step 2: Apply to join the campaign here: https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeONaanQP3QfWLeNKAqCC9IQv4nN_qgK2ekOufQ-mnbcsxWEw/viewform - Follow our official Twitter Account : https://twitter.com/bitscreener  - Only one twitter account per person is allowed. - You have to share at least 2 different crypto charts on your Twitter from BitScreener.Com by following the instructions: https://medium.com/@BitScreener/how-to-share-a-crypto-chart-on-twitter-e587cd37e5c8 - You have to retweet and like at least 3 different tweets per week from our Official Twitter account. Make your own tweets if we don't have enough tweets this week - Do not retweet anything older than 4 days, it will NOT be counted if it's done multiple times, you will be banned. - You have to post at least 2 different tweets per week about BitScreener products (Website, iOS & Android app) and BitScreener ICO. Max 1 tweet per day. Tweets and Retweets have to be spaced at least 1 hour. Anyone breaking this rule will be banned from the bounty campaign Everyone must use 2 hashtags for tweets: #BitScreener and #BITX Follower count will be fixed when you sign up for this program You must reported your works in this thread every week with the following format:   Deadline to report: 11:59PM UTC every Sunday Note: We check tweets and retweets manually, so please be patient.  Rewards: 200-1999 real followers: 70 stakes/week 2000 and above: 100 stakes/week    Facebook Campaign (Started on Jul 23rd) Facebook Instructions:  How to Join: Step 1: Post a new message here with your BitcoinTalk username, profile link, Telegram ID & ETH Address to confirm your identity We will check this info manually to send Tokens to the right person later Step 2: Apply to join the campaign here: https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScegUgbLsPTflyPqvVoEhMj5hR3ff70n3ef0OHF_yjtpZJzZg/viewform Follow and Like the official Facebook page: https://www.facebook.com/bitscreenercom Only one Facebook account per person is allowed. Users must have at least 200 friends and number of friends must be public You have to share & like at least 3 different posts per week from our official facebook page. Make your own posts if we don't have enough posts this week Shared posts have to be spaced at least 1 hour. Anyone breaking this rule will be banned from the bounty campaign Do not share posts older than 4 days, it will NOT be counted if it's done multiple times, you will be banned. Friends  count will be fixed when you sign up for this program You must reported your works in this thread every week with the following format:  Week: ___ Facebook profile link: ___ Likes and Shares: ___ ETH wallet address: ___ Deadline to report: 11:59PM UTC every Sunday  Rewards: 200-1999 real friends: 70 stakes/week 2000 and above: 100 stakes/week        [ENDED ON JUL 5TH 2018]BitScreener is starting its OFFICIAL BOUNTY PROGRAM in order to reward its supporters. A total of 6,500,000 BITX tokens ($680,000) generated will be assigned to the Bounty Pool   [ENDED ON JUL 5TH 2018] General Info  Participants in the bounty program will be rewarded with STAKES. Bounty Program Start Date: May 07, 2018 Bounty Program End Date: Jul 5th, 2018 Total number of tokens allocated to the bounty program: 6,500,000 BITX ($680,000) If the total number of stakes earned during the program doesn’t exceed the cap: 1 STAKE=1 BITX.   If not, we will adjust your stakes based on the below formula: (Total number of tokens/total number of stakes everyone earned during the program)* number of stakes you earned= Your final number of BITX    [ENDED ON JUL 5TH 2018] The tokens will be distributed in 6 campaigns as follows:  BitScreener Mobile App Referral (20%) - ENDED Twitter Bounty (15%) - ENDED Facebook Bounty (15%) - ENDED Telegram Bounty (15%) - ENDED BitcoinTalk signature campaign (15%) - ENDED Content (blogs and media publications) (10%) - ENDED Translation Bounty (10%) - ENDED    Check your stakes on this SPREADSHEET     Mobile App Referral Instructions:  How to Join: Step 1: Download iOS or Android app iOS app link: https://apple.co/2Khn4pF Android app link: http://[Suspicious link removed]/2rCexGJ Step 2: Open the app => Go to the tab More => tap the button "Get FREE BitScreener Tokens" Step 3: Login and enter your ETH address (you will never lose your stakes if you login again with the same account) Step 4: Use the link generated to invite your friends.  Rules: 1 friend invited = 50 BITX STAKES (1ETH = 7156 BITX) Referred devices had never installed BitScreener app before, open it right after installing the app & MUST KEEP THE APP UNTIL THE END OF THIS CAMPAIGN (If not you will lose all the stakes) Stakes will be counted weekly and updated in the spreadsheet link above. Plus LIFETIME PREMIUM ACCESS to all BitScreener mobile products (iOS & Android apps) if you get more than 8000 BITX in this campaign Any account that violates this rules will be banned and will not receive any BITX on any campaign We reserve the right to change the rules if necessary by updating this thread. Please always read carefully before asking questions. For questions: contact admins on our official Telegram group (https://t.me/bitscreener)      Twitter Campaign Twitter Instructions:  How to Join: Step 1: Post a new message here with your BitcoinTalk username, profile link, Telegram ID & ETH Address to confirm your identity We will check this info manually to send Tokens to the right person later Step 2: Apply to join the campaign here: https://[Suspicious link removed]/forms/I6QcNrR1Lq29tJ2N2 Follow our official Twitter Account : https://twitter.com/bitscreener Your twitter account must have at least 200 real followers Only one twitter account per person is allowed. You have to retweet and like at least 3 different tweets per week from our Official Twitter account. Make your own tweets if we don't have enough tweets this week Do not retweet anything older than 4 days, it will NOT be counted if it's done multiple times, you will be banned. You have to post at least 2 different tweets per week about BitScreener products (Website, iOS & Android app) and BitScreener ICO. Max 1 tweet per day. Tweets and Retweets have to be spaced at least 1 hour. Anyone breaking this rule will be banned from the bounty campaign Everyone must use 2 hashtags for tweets, 1 #BitScreener and 2nd one of the #ICO, #BITX Follower count will be fixed when you sign up for bounty Tweets must be in English and must be posted in this thread every week. Deadline to report: 11:59PM every Sunday (local time) Note: We check tweets and retweets manually, so please be patient.  Rewards: 200-1999 real followers: 70 stakes/week 2000 and above: 100 stakes/week    Facebook Campaign Facebook Instructions:  How to Join: Step 1: Post a new message here with your BitcoinTalk username, profile link, Telegram ID & ETH Address to confirm your identity We will check this info manually to send Tokens to the right person later Step 2: Apply to join the campaign here: https://[Suspicious link removed]/forms/B8EG40tMWUXfjTHU2 Follow and Like the official Facebook page: https://www.facebook.com/bitscreenercom Only one Facebook account per person is allowed. Users must have at least 200 friends and number of friends must be public You have to share & like at least 3 different posts per week from our official facebook page. Make your own posts if we don't have enough posts this week Shared posts have to be spaced at least 1 hour. Anyone breaking this rule will be banned from the bounty campaign Do not share posts older than 4 days, it will NOT be counted if it's done multiple times, you will be banned. Friends  count will be fixed when you sign up for bounty Posts must be in English, public and viewable, and must be posted in this thread every week. Deadline to report: 11:59PM every Sunday (local time)  Rewards: 200-1999 real friends: 70 stakes/week 2000 and above: 100 stakes/week     Telegram Campaign - ENDED Telegram Instructions:  A maximum of 1 post per week is allowed in each Telegram group Groups with fake members will be disqualified. We will check groups manually.  How to Join: Step 1: Post a new message here with your BitcoinTalk username, profile link, Telegram ID & ETH Address to confirm your identity We will check this info manually to send Tokens to the right person later Step 2: Join BitScreener Telegram: https://t.me/bitscreener Step 3: Apply to join the campaign here: https://[Suspicious link removed]/forms/W8JWxfFqfgFBkPuz1 Step 4: Post messages on crypto related Telegram groups Message content must contain your own words about advantages of BitScreener running products over similar products  or advantages of BitScreener ICO over other ICOs and the link to our token sale website: https://tokensale.bitscreener.com?utm_source=telegram&utm_medium=bounty  See the following example:  https://tokensale.bitscreener.com?utm_source=telegram&utm_medium=bounty BitScreener is the #1 crypto tracker used by millions of users with a lot of unique features like: screeners, advanced alerts & signals, real-time portfolios, etc. Now they are launching a very promising ICO project to become the the world's first financial data ecosystem powered by blockchain Messages must be posted in crypto related groups Upload the screenshot (using imgur, postimage or similar) and report it in this thread every week Deadline to report: 11:59PM every Sunday (local time)  Stakes: 100-299 Members: 2 stakes/post/week 300-699 Members: 4 stakes/post/week 700-1999 Members: 6 stakes/post/week 2000+ Members: 8 stakes/post/week Note: Maximum: 200 stakes/account/week    BitcoinTalk Signature Campaign - ENDED Signature Instructions:  How to Join: Step 1: Post a new message here with your BitcoinTalk username, profile link, Telegram ID & ETH Address to confirm your identity We will check this info manually to send Tokens to the right person later Step 2: Apply to join the campaign here: https://[Suspicious link removed]/forms/wHLZY7iMgvtHA36V2 Posts in this thread will not count. No negative Trust. No multiple Signatures. Posts in following Discussion Boards will not be counted: Politics and Society, Off-topic, Archival, Auctions, Lending, Beginners and help. No Spam, Abuse or Insults.  Terms and conditions: Only for Junior members and above. Make at least 5 posts each week during the week. Posts in alternate cryptocurrencies section are required. The posts should be spread for the full week, not for just 1-2 days otherwise your stake will be 0 for the week. Posts in any bounty thread will not be counted. Spam is strictly prohibited. Users found spamming will be immediately and permanently disqualified, reported to the moderators, and banned from any other bounty campaign. Report you work in this thread every week. Deadline to report: 11:59PM every Sunday (local time)  Rewards: Junior Members :       30 stakes per week Members :                60 stakes per week Full Members :          150 stakes per week Senior Members :      250 stakes per week Legendary/Hero:       400 stakes per week 20 stakes extra for avatar and personal text  Get the signature here and avatar here    Blog Article & Videos Campaign - ENDED Important Content Guidelines: Describe BitScreener running products: iOS app, Android app, and website BitScrener.com BitScreener, a working product, is unlike other ICOs - here's how Unique features of BitScreener running products compared with other products How will the BITX (BitScreener utility token) be used for services within the Ecosystem Your experience as a user of BitScreener How BITX will benefit millions of BitScreener users How to become a BITX “miner” to get BITX? Top 5 features of BitScreener How do you buy BITX in BitScreener's ICO  Article writing instructions:  How to Join: Step 1: Post a new message here with your BitcoinTalk username, profile link, Telegram ID & ETH Address to confirm your identity We will check this info manually to send Tokens to the right person later Step 2: Write a good article, review, or blog post about BitScreener  in your words; Post that on your website or blog. The article/review/blog post must have at least 500 words. Your text must be original. Copy and stealing other contents bring to disqualification. The audience for the posted article must be crypto related or match a use for BitScreener or promote BitScreener ICO to a suitable audience. Website must have a genuine audience. New websites will not be accepted. Article/review/blog post must contain link to the BitScreener  website, BitScreener  telegram group and BitScreener official twitter. Writers should familiarize themselves with the official white papers to ensure an accurate depiction of BitScreener Token (BITX) uses.  Rewards: For Original article BIG {2000 words or more} = 800 stake For Original article MEDIUM {1000-2000 words} = 500 Stake For Original article SMALL {Below 1000 words} = 300 stake (Multiple articles accepted but maximum 3000 stakes per account)  Video instructions:  How to Join: Step 1: Post a new message here with your BitcoinTalk username, profile link, Telegram ID & ETH Address to confirm your identity We will check this info manually to send Tokens to the right person later Step 2: Describe about advantages of BitScreener products and BitScreener ICO project Video must be in a good resolution Video must be minimum 2 minutes. You will receive rewards based on the number of views  Rewards: 800+ views:  800 stake 200 - 800 views:  500 stake 20 - 200 views:  300 stake (Multiple videos accepted but maximum 3000 stakes per account)  Inform us about your Article/Videos here: https://[Suspicious link removed]/forms/wg1pBIkBYNmcKDCQ2    Translation Campaign - ENDED Translation Instructions:  How to Join: Step 1: Post a new message here with your BitcoinTalk username, profile link, Telegram ID & ETH Address to confirm your identity We will check this info manually to send Tokens to the right person later Step 2: Apply to join the campaign here: https://[Suspicious link removed]/forms/NxKN1DSfuUpt9BMk1 Using Google Translate and other online translators are not allowed. Participants using Google Translate will be instantly disqualified. Applications for the translations to multiple languages will not be accepted. Participants must fill the form and accepted translator will get confirmation by Telegram Message. We need active participation from translators in their local threads. Bounty will be deducted if thread became dead.  Rewards: Translation of Whitepaper : 1000 Stakes Proofreading of Whitepaper : 300 Stakes Translation of ANN/Bounty thread to your language : 200 Stakes Proofreading of ANN/Bounty thread to your language : 100 Stakes Translation of texts on the BitScreener iOS app: 200 States Proofreading of texts on the BitScreener iOS app: 100 States      General Bounty Rules  All bounty participants are required to join BitScreener’s Telegram group: https://t.me/bitscreener Each user can only participate in one account per campaign. All campaigns will be counted weekly. All rewards for bounty activities will be STAKES tokens. If you are disqualified for any reason, you will NOT receive any bounty rewards. The BitScreener team will reserve the right to change any rules, or make any changes, if necessary For technical support during the bounty campaign, please contact us via our Telegram group All tokens will be allocated to your Ethereum wallet within 30 days of the BitScreener token contribution event end date.
